actions.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

official_title: A bill to extend until January 1, 1995, the existing suspension of duty on Cefixime.

summary.text: Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend, through December 31, 1994, the suspension of duty on (6R-(6a,7B(Z)))-7-(((2- amino -4-thiazolyl)((carboxymethoxy)imino) acetyl)amino)-3 ethenyl-8-oxo-5-thia-1-azabicyclo (4.2.0)- oct-2-ene-2-carboxylic acid (also known as cefixime).

titles.title: A bill to extend until January 1, 1995, the existing suspension of duty on Cefixime.
